    "body": "This is up-to-date [Flashbots docs link](https://docs.flashbots.net/flashbots-auction/searchers/advanced/rpc-endpoint#eth_callbundle) (as of today) \r\n\r\nAnd here is the [mev-geth](https://github.com/flashbots/mev-geth) repo. Look at the `CallBundle` API implementation starting [this line](https://github.com/flashbots/mev-geth/blob/master/internal/ethapi/api.go#L2067)\r\n\r\nIt would indeed have been great to have the `eth_callBundle` ported, or reimplement something relatively similar (the callBundle logic may be a bit involved with the Flashbots \"bundles\" concept etc.) HTH!\r\n\r\n\r\n",
